OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779289870
OL,3,CTeenager arrested after attempted
OL,4,Cmurder leaving man in critical
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FA teenager has been arrested as part
OL,8,Fof an attempted murder investigation.
OL,10,FThe 17-year-old boy, from Stafford,
OL,11,Fwas arrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,12,Fmurder last night and remains in
OL,13,Fpolice custody.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Ian
OL,16,FFitzgerald from Staffordshire Police
OL,17,Fsaid: "The arrest is a significant
OL,18,Fdevelopment in our investigation which
OL,19,Fcontinues at pace.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
