OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779289870
OL,3,CTeenager arrested after attempted
OL,4,Cmurder leaving man in critical
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,F"I have a range of specialist
OL,8,Fresources dedicated to this
OL,9,Finvestigation. The victim remains in
OL,10,Fhospital in a critical but stable
OL,11,Fcondition. His family are being
OL,12,Fsupported by our family liaison
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
