PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779289870
OL,3,CTeenager arrested after attempted
OL,4,Cmurder leaving man in critical
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,F"The response from the community has
OL,8,Fbeen invaluable with lots of people
OL,9,Fsharing information and CCTV footage.
OL,10,FHowever, I must ask people not to use
OL,11,FAI or other software to enhance any of
OL,12,Fthe images we have shared. It is
OL,13,Fincredibly harmful to our
OL,14,Finvestigation, particularly when
OL,15,Farrests have been made and legal
OL,16,Fproceedings are active."
OL,18,FThe 30-year-old man who was questioned
OL,19,Fin connection with this investigation
OL,20,Fhas since been released on conditional
OL,21,Fbail.
